1. *Bježi* što dalje odavde! (Run away as far as you can from here!)
2. Otkako je vidjela zmiju, ona *bježi* iz svog dvorišta. (Since she saw the snake, she's been running away from her yard.)
3. Ja ne mogu *bježati* od svojih problema zauvijek. (I can't run away from my problems forever.)
4. *Bježali* su od policije nakon što su ukrali bicikle. (They ran away from the police after stealing bicycles.)
5. Moramo *pobjeći* iz ovog grada jer se ne osjećam sigurno ovdje. (We have to escape from this city because I don't feel safe here.)
6. Oni su *pobjegli* s koncerta prije kraja. (They escaped from the concert before it ended.)
7. Zbog iznenadne kiše, morali smo *bježati* po kiši do automobila. (Because of the sudden rain, we had to run in the rain to the car.)
8. Kada je vidio medvjeda, on je brzo *pobjegao* u šumu. (When he saw the bear, he quickly ran away into the forest.)
9. *Bježeći* iz kuće, ona je slučajno zaboravila ključeve. (While running away from the house, she accidentally forgot the keys.)
10. Oni su *bježali* jedan za drugim kroz park. (They were running away from each other through the park.)